for verbose output
curl -v http://localhost:9090 

to send data using curl
curl -v -d 'hello' http://localhost:9090

to send a delete request
curl http://localhost:9090 -XDELETE -v| jq

to send a put request
curl -v http://localhost:9090/1 -XPUT
curl -v http://localhost:9090/1 -d '{"id":1, "name":"tea", "description":"a nice cup of tea"}' -XPUT

to send a post request
curl -v http://localhost:9090 -d '{"id":1, "name":"tea", "description":"a nice cup of tea"}' -XPOST

curl -v "http://localhost:9090/products?currency=USD"